# Build context = repo root. Exclude anything that doesn't need to ship to
# the Docker daemon's build kit (each MB increases build-time + memory).

**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.vite
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/*.tsbuildinfo

.git
.github
.claude
.vscode
.idea

# Secrets and per-machine state
.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*
secrets/

# Repo docs / metadata not needed inside the image
docs
memory-seeds
systemd
scripts
roadmap
docker
README.md
AGENTS.md
ARCHITECTURE.md
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.md.tmpl
AGENT-LOG.md
REVIEW-LOG.md
ROADMAP.md
LICENSE
.mcp.json
.mcp.json.tmpl
